1029
01:28:38,953 --> 01:28:43,113
<i>The way she speaks the truth.</i>

1030
01:28:43,123 --> 01:28:45,813
<i>The way she sees the world.</i>

1031
01:28:47,763 --> 01:28:50,793
<i>And I pray that never changes.</i>

1032
01:28:51,463 --> 01:28:55,163
<i>Now, Renee was
supposed to be here tonight.</i>

1033
01:28:56,033 --> 01:28:58,163
