1042
01:29:38,172 --> 01:29:42,642
<i>and I found the To Write Love site.</i>

1043
01:29:43,082 --> 01:29:44,812
<i>I read Renee's story.</i>

1044
01:29:45,982 --> 01:29:50,082
<i>I wasn't used to hearing
other people hurting.</i>

1045
01:29:50,592 --> 01:29:53,922
<i>Her story helped me find hope.</i>

1046
01:29:55,962 --> 01:29:57,492
<i>Thank you.</i>

1047
