1053
01:30:19,221 --> 01:30:22,981
<i>and I know they're worried about me.</i>

1054
01:30:24,551 --> 01:30:28,951
<i>They think I'm better, and I'm not.</i>

1055
01:30:29,761 --> 01:30:33,821
