1097
01:34:56,986 --> 01:34:58,916
<i>Rescue is possible.</i>

1098
01:34:59,156 --> 01:35:01,416
<i>God is still in the business of redemption.</i>

1099
01:35:03,066 --> 01:35:06,726
<i>The first step to recovery
